title: Guided By Voices 09-02-94 CST
description:
Guided By Voices, September 2nd, 1994 AUD recording by Scott Nuckles / \"Chapter 18\" of DtS.

This may have been Jim Greer\&#039;s debut on bass as evidenced by Pollard\&#039;s quote \"Give it up for our new bass player Jim Greer\"

Lots of classics from the forthcoming, \"Scalping the Guru\" LP / Alien Lanes LP, Bee Thousand, and a few rarities from the EP\&#039;s of the same era.  This is a great setlist.  The vocals are a bit muddy...but no worries as we all know the lyrics anyway  :)

Once again BIG THANKS to Scott Nuckles / \"Chapter 18\" from DtS for taping this and sharing it with us!

Long live GBV!
